      "title": "Sri Lanka to donate 6Mn Pfizer doses to Myanmar",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka has decided to donate 6 million doses of Pfizer vaccines to Myanmar.",
        "The Ministry of Health stated that the relevant agreement will be inked next week.",
        "The donation will take place with the intervention of the World Health Organization.",
        "The stock of Pfizer vaccine doses purchased in Sri Lanka for COVID-19 vaccination is set to expire within the next two months."
      ],
